WEBVTT

00:00:13.113 --> 00:00:14.781
Hello?

00:00:14.781 --> 00:00:17.515
Aren't we skipping class together today?
Where were you?

00:00:17.515 --> 00:00:19.519
- Where's the turtle drawing?
- It's in my bag.

00:00:19.519 --> 00:00:21.354
Can I have it?

00:00:21.354 --> 00:00:23.855
What are you doing?
Where on earth were you today?

00:00:23.855 --> 00:00:26.025
I've been waiting for so long.

00:00:28.028 --> 00:00:29.762
What's going on?

00:00:30.997 --> 00:00:32.399
What are you doing?

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:35.099
Hey, what are you doing?
What are you doing?

00:00:35.099 --> 00:00:37.203
What are you doing?

00:00:39.806 --> 00:00:41.607
What's wrong with you?

00:00:43.410 --> 00:00:45.879
What are you doing?

00:00:45.879 --> 00:00:47.447
I heard everything.

00:00:47.447 --> 00:00:49.716
Heard what?

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:52.185
Whatever, I'm just a loser.

00:00:52.185 --> 00:00:55.254
I'm just a country bumpkin
you all look down on.

00:00:56.389 --> 00:01:01.027
No matter what we do, we just get scolded.

00:01:01.027 --> 00:01:03.396
We're never liked.

00:01:03.396 --> 00:01:05.564
But I've tried my best.

00:01:06.499 --> 00:01:08.168
But I never succeed.

00:01:08.168 --> 00:01:09.769
Unlike you.

00:01:09.769 --> 00:01:13.006
No matter what you do, everyone praises you.

00:01:13.006 --> 00:01:14.641
Everyone says you're great.

00:01:14.641 --> 00:01:16.709
And you're never lonely.

00:01:18.311 --> 00:01:20.780
But I'm different.

00:01:20.780 --> 00:01:23.682
I've been an island kid since I was little.

00:01:24.551 --> 00:01:27.353
We never had time to study.

00:01:29.355 --> 00:01:31.991
No one ever wanted to be my friend.

00:01:31.991 --> 00:01:35.028
That's why I drew all by myself.

00:01:35.028 --> 00:01:36.696
Thanks for accepting such a lousy gift.

00:01:36.696 --> 00:01:38.230
I...

00:01:38.832 --> 00:01:40.467
She and I are just... We're just...

00:01:40.467 --> 00:01:41.634
I was just going along with what she said.

00:01:41.634 --> 00:01:42.769
I was just trying to brush her off.

00:01:42.769 --> 00:01:45.071
- Brush her off?
- I really didn't mean it.

00:01:45.071 --> 00:01:46.139
So, this is how you treat your friends?

00:01:46.139 --> 00:01:47.674
By just brushing them off like that?

00:01:47.674 --> 00:01:51.077
She and I aren't even friends.

00:01:51.077 --> 00:01:53.179
How can I believe anything you say?

00:01:53.179 --> 00:01:55.181
Maybe you're just doing this because
you don't want to ruin the relationship.

00:01:55.181 --> 00:01:57.817
You're just being casual and dismissive.

00:01:57.817 --> 00:01:59.686
There's really nothing between us.

00:01:59.686 --> 00:02:02.021
Chen Hao Wei.

00:02:02.021 --> 00:02:05.026
Thank you for letting me
have such a beautiful dream.

00:02:05.026 --> 00:02:06.058
What do you mean?

00:02:06.058 --> 00:02:08.929
Now that the dream is over,
it's time for me to leave.

00:02:08.929 --> 00:02:09.929
- What do you mean?
- Don't come looking for me again.

00:02:09.929 --> 00:02:11.131
-

00:02:11.131 --> 00:02:12.131
- What are you talking about?
- Just pretend I don't exist, okay?

00:02:12.131 --> 00:02:14.567
-

00:02:14.567 --> 00:02:15.768
He Xiang Yong.

00:02:15.768 --> 00:02:18.771
We simply don't belong in the same world.

00:02:18.771 --> 00:02:20.740
I don't understand.

00:02:20.740 --> 00:02:22.675
You can keep on smiling now.

00:02:22.675 --> 00:02:25.912
Without me around,
you'll be able to smile even more.

00:02:25.912 --> 00:02:27.680
What on earth are you saying, He Xiang Yong?

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:29.581
He Xiang Yong!

00:02:40.693 --> 00:02:43.295
What's wrong with you?

00:02:46.199 --> 00:02:48.367
He Xiang Yong!

00:02:49.435 --> 00:02:51.837
He Xiang Yong!

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:56.208
He Xiang Yong!

00:03:00.947 --> 00:03:03.583
He Xiang Yong!

00:03:03.583 --> 00:03:05.985
He Xiang Yong!

00:04:08.481 --> 00:04:09.983
Mr. He.

00:04:09.983 --> 00:04:11.150
- Let us have a drink with you.
- Sure.

00:04:11.150 --> 00:04:12.151
-

00:04:12.151 --> 00:04:13.952
Come on, let's have a drink.

00:04:16.256 --> 00:04:17.657
Come on.

00:04:17.657 --> 00:04:19.258
Drink up.

00:04:27.667 --> 00:04:29.635
I've decided to go back to the main island.

00:04:31.204 --> 00:04:32.838
You're quitting?

00:04:34.474 --> 00:04:36.575
Why the sudden departure?

00:04:42.715 --> 00:04:46.552
Actually, my vacation has come to an end.

00:04:46.552 --> 00:04:49.956
My company has been pressuring me
to return to work.

00:04:49.956 --> 00:04:51.957
I can't delay it any longer.

00:04:53.726 --> 00:04:56.496
Mr. He, I'm sorry.

00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:58.031
I made this decision
without consulting you first.

00:04:58.031 --> 00:05:01.200
What are you apologizing for?

00:05:01.200 --> 00:05:04.270
You've helped me out so much.

00:05:04.270 --> 00:05:07.507
Besides, with everything
that's happened at the inn lately,

00:05:07.507 --> 00:05:10.509
I'm sure it was hard for you to bring up.

00:05:12.779 --> 00:05:14.547
Go on, head back.

00:05:14.547 --> 00:05:16.983
This is just a place for you youngsters

00:05:16.983 --> 00:05:19.652
to take a breather and rest for a while.

00:05:19.652 --> 00:05:22.322
Go back and work hard for your future.

00:05:22.322 --> 00:05:24.691
When you're tired, remember to come back.

00:05:24.691 --> 00:05:27.760
You've got me,
that old rascal Hua, and Angela here.

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:29.996
Eat up and nourish yourself.

00:05:29.996 --> 00:05:31.663
Okay.

00:05:32.465 --> 00:05:34.366
Thank you, Mr. He.

00:05:39.138 --> 00:05:41.273
What about me?

00:05:42.442 --> 00:05:45.010
Do you have anything to say to me?

00:05:49.048 --> 00:05:50.817
You?

00:05:50.817 --> 00:05:52.684
Just take good care of the inn.

00:06:00.526 --> 00:06:01.528
What's with that face? Come on.

00:06:01.528 --> 00:06:04.430
Let's raise our glasses and drink. Come on.

00:06:04.430 --> 00:06:06.430
You guys drink. I don't want to.

00:06:06.430 --> 00:06:08.033
Fine, don't drink then. Come on, let's drink.

00:06:08.033 --> 00:06:09.868
Thank you, Mr. He.

00:06:20.766 --> 00:06:22.178
Thank you.

00:06:22.178 --> 00:06:24.314
[Ladder Steps]

00:06:40.833 --> 00:06:42.068
Li Wan Zhe.

00:06:42.068 --> 00:06:44.837
Do you really think you're some
young master of the Li family?

00:06:44.837 --> 00:06:46.806
Why are you giving all the work to Hama-chan?

00:06:46.806 --> 00:06:48.207
I'm didn't.

00:06:48.207 --> 00:06:49.209
I've been working. Counting money.

00:06:49.209 --> 00:06:50.209
-

00:06:50.209 --> 00:06:51.811
Supervising.

00:06:51.811 --> 00:06:53.846
Auntie, don't scold him.

00:06:53.846 --> 00:06:56.181
I was the one who told him to rest.

00:06:57.316 --> 00:07:00.385
I haven't even started scolding him yet.

00:07:01.821 --> 00:07:03.555
What are you laughing at?

00:07:06.459 --> 00:07:09.028
You're letting him do all the work.

00:07:09.028 --> 00:07:10.463
- Don't you feel any shame?
- What should I be ashamed of?

00:07:10.463 --> 00:07:11.497
-

00:07:11.497 --> 00:07:14.132
Hama-chan told me to take a break himself.

00:07:15.835 --> 00:07:17.570
It's strange.

00:07:17.570 --> 00:07:19.705
Hama-chan was out at sea with Mr. Zhong.

00:07:19.705 --> 00:07:21.874
The pay and benefits were quite good.

00:07:21.874 --> 00:07:23.676
Why would he give that up?

00:07:23.676 --> 00:07:26.377
Maybe Hama-chan thinks
our family's benefits are even better.

00:07:26.377 --> 00:07:27.079
-

00:07:30.783 --> 00:07:32.618
Are you talking about yourself?

00:07:35.755 --> 00:07:38.558
He must be possessed. Good grief.

00:07:38.558 --> 00:07:41.059
Forget it. I'm not going to
bother with you guys.

00:07:41.861 --> 00:07:44.030
- There's a lot today.
- Yeah, 8,700 in total.

00:07:44.030 --> 00:07:46.064
Not a penny short.

00:07:49.769 --> 00:07:52.238
Let's find a different spot next time.

00:07:52.238 --> 00:07:56.272
All right. I'm off to enjoy my adult nightlife.

00:07:58.377 --> 00:08:01.077
Wait, Mom!
You're only leaving me the change?

00:08:01.077 --> 00:08:01.813
-

00:08:02.582 --> 00:08:05.150
Li Wan Zhe, are you hungry?

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.488
You've worked hard all day.

00:08:08.488 --> 00:08:10.922
I'll make you a late-night snack.

00:08:12.925 --> 00:08:14.660
Sure. Okay.

00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:16.995
I'll wash up quickly.

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:23.101
Is it really related to the shooting star?

00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:10.349
Why do you have the turtle drawing?

00:09:13.085 --> 00:09:15.688
Didn't you tear it up back then?

00:09:15.688 --> 00:09:17.857
Why did you piece it back together?

00:09:17.857 --> 00:09:20.726
And why keep it for so long?

00:09:20.726 --> 00:09:23.495
What do you mean
by wanting me to give it to him?

00:09:26.732 --> 00:09:29.702
It seems you two are really close.

00:09:29.702 --> 00:09:32.938
He even told you about the turtle drawing.

00:09:39.045 --> 00:09:43.614
I thought that was a story just between him and me.

00:09:43.614 --> 00:09:44.282
-

00:09:46.852 --> 00:09:48.887
You and him?

00:09:50.323 --> 00:09:52.524
You mean you and the others.

00:09:54.026 --> 00:09:57.062
Didn't you join the others in mocking him?

00:09:58.864 --> 00:10:01.899
Do you know how much his heart ached
when he heard those words?

00:10:01.899 --> 00:10:02.701
-

00:10:08.808 --> 00:10:10.475
It wasn't like that.

00:10:13.045 --> 00:10:15.313
Back then...

00:10:18.284 --> 00:10:20.553
I cared too much about what others thought.

00:10:20.553 --> 00:10:23.221
I wanted to please everyone too much.

00:10:24.390 --> 00:10:26.225
For the past ten years,

00:10:26.225 --> 00:10:28.627
I haven't spent a single day without regret.

00:10:29.528 --> 00:10:32.464
I really want to apologize to him.

00:10:46.379 --> 00:10:48.747
If you regret it so much,

00:10:50.383 --> 00:10:54.053
why did you wait until now to find him?

00:10:54.053 --> 00:10:55.888
I was afraid that if I went to him,

00:10:55.888 --> 00:10:58.356
it would only cause him resentment.

00:11:00.226 --> 00:11:05.764
It seems Starry Islet is still on his side.

00:11:08.300 --> 00:11:12.647
He clearly came back,
but we still missed each other.

00:11:17.543 --> 00:11:22.512
Then is there anything you want to say to him?

00:11:22.512 --> 00:11:23.081
-

00:11:24.884 --> 00:11:28.787
I can pass the message to him.

00:11:36.128 --> 00:11:39.231
He said this place is a turtle's paradise.

00:11:43.769 --> 00:11:46.404
I fixed the turtle drawing

00:11:48.040 --> 00:11:51.276
hoping to mend his broken heart as well.

00:11:53.312 --> 00:11:56.248
I hope he can find his paradise.

00:12:04.490 --> 00:12:07.292
I don't ask for his forgiveness.

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:14.065
I just hope he can be happy every day.

00:12:25.945 --> 00:12:29.381
He's always been the best artist in my heart.

00:12:30.249 --> 00:12:33.051
And the best He Xiang Yong.

00:12:52.905 --> 00:12:55.774
I believe after he hears what you said,

00:12:56.408 --> 00:12:58.743
he will definitely forgive you.

00:13:01.347 --> 00:13:02.815
In his life...

00:13:02.815 --> 00:13:05.483
Although he often failed,

00:13:06.585 --> 00:13:10.422
I think, at least in your heart,

00:13:11.690 --> 00:13:14.759
he's still at the top of the list, right?

00:13:15.961 --> 00:13:18.196
Sometimes...

00:13:20.199 --> 00:13:22.990
I really think you're a lot like He Xiang Yong.

00:13:41.287 --> 00:13:43.489
Chen Hao Wei.

00:13:43.489 --> 00:13:47.525
Just how much time did you spend doing this?

00:13:57.303 --> 00:13:59.270
Come on.

00:14:05.144 --> 00:14:08.380
Hao Wei is going back
to the main island for work.

00:14:08.380 --> 00:14:12.215
That means from now on,
we'll have one less hunk to help out.

00:14:12.215 --> 00:14:13.084
-

00:14:13.719 --> 00:14:16.088
You have to hang in there.

00:14:16.088 --> 00:14:18.123
My retirement depends on you.

00:14:18.123 --> 00:14:21.193
This inn can't go under.

00:14:21.193 --> 00:14:23.694
I used to run it all by myself.
Did it ever go under?

00:14:23.694 --> 00:14:24.295
-

00:14:25.331 --> 00:14:27.433
I've already bought this place.

00:14:27.433 --> 00:14:29.501
Are you here to pick a fight or to drink?

00:14:29.501 --> 00:14:30.603
Fine, fine.

00:14:30.603 --> 00:14:32.137
Always nagging.

00:14:32.137 --> 00:14:34.573
Have you thought about
asking Xiang Yong to come back and help?

00:14:34.573 --> 00:14:36.909
Of course I have.
But I don't even know where he is.

00:14:36.909 --> 00:14:38.010
Forget it.

00:14:38.010 --> 00:14:40.512
He'll come back when he's ready.

00:14:40.512 --> 00:14:44.450
I'm telling you,
you spoil your son way too much.

00:14:44.450 --> 00:14:46.452
If my son dared to do that,

00:14:46.452 --> 00:14:49.622
please, you guys better call 113 for him.

00:14:49.622 --> 00:14:51.823
To save him, okay?

00:14:53.125 --> 00:14:55.394
I'm not spoiling him.

00:14:55.394 --> 00:14:58.097
I just understand him.

00:14:58.097 --> 00:15:00.799
He's hated being forced since he was a kid.

00:15:00.799 --> 00:15:02.467
He's like when you push a ball underwater.

00:15:02.467 --> 00:15:03.302
-

00:15:03.302 --> 00:15:05.970
The deeper you push, the higher it bounces.

00:15:07.139 --> 00:15:09.441
- Is that so?
- Of course it is.

00:15:09.441 --> 00:15:10.709
Once, I caught him drawing in secret.

00:15:10.709 --> 00:15:12.378
I confiscated all his art supplies.

00:15:12.378 --> 00:15:13.779
So, he used a rock,

00:15:13.779 --> 00:15:15.747
and right under the chair you're sitting on,
he drew an entire zoo.

00:15:15.747 --> 00:15:16.649
-

00:15:16.649 --> 00:15:18.683
See how talented he is?

00:15:34.433 --> 00:15:36.967
Why don't I remember that?
Was it after I arrived?

00:15:36.967 --> 00:15:37.836
-

00:15:37.836 --> 00:15:40.139
Are you so old that you can't remember?

00:15:40.139 --> 00:15:41.874
That one time he had a fever of 104 degrees.

00:15:41.874 --> 00:15:43.309
He was still drawing under the covers.

00:15:43.309 --> 00:15:45.411
I got so mad I took away his art supplies.

00:15:45.411 --> 00:15:48.047
Did you forget? You were right there.

00:15:48.047 --> 00:15:50.148
Did that really happen?

00:15:50.983 --> 00:15:52.584
See for yourself.

00:15:52.584 --> 00:15:54.385
Take a look.

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:57.956
- Where?
- There's nothing.

00:15:59.091 --> 00:16:01.694
Nothing? You're in trouble.

00:16:01.694 --> 00:16:04.263
Maybe you should eat more ginkgo nuts.

00:16:04.263 --> 00:16:06.665
Or fish oil or something.

00:16:06.665 --> 00:16:08.067
Could it be that your wife
replaced all the tables and chairs,

00:16:08.067 --> 00:16:09.568
-

00:16:09.568 --> 00:16:12.103
and you just forgot?

00:16:13.539 --> 00:16:15.874
How is that possible?

00:16:17.443 --> 00:16:18.610
Come on, drink up.

00:16:18.610 --> 00:16:21.479
I'm getting old.

00:16:41.982 --> 00:16:46.137
[Home is He-re]

00:17:10.596 --> 00:17:14.632
I've realized that we have
good working rapport.

00:17:15.300 --> 00:17:18.068
After you leave,
Mr. He will definitely think I'm clumsy.

00:17:18.068 --> 00:17:18.937
-

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:23.342
Why would he?

00:17:23.342 --> 00:17:25.311
Your garlic shrimp noodles is so good. Right?

00:17:25.311 --> 00:17:26.311
-

00:17:26.311 --> 00:17:28.246
Mr. He likes it so much.

00:17:30.149 --> 00:17:32.017
What about Mr. Hua?

00:17:32.017 --> 00:17:33.786
You always go fishing with him.

00:17:33.786 --> 00:17:37.055
Without you, he'll probably feel very lonely.

00:17:39.091 --> 00:17:40.793
With Mr. He around,

00:17:40.793 --> 00:17:42.127
and Angela here, too,

00:17:42.127 --> 00:17:44.562
how could he be lonely with all of you?

00:17:46.065 --> 00:17:47.132
That's true.

00:17:47.132 --> 00:17:48.903
Speaking of Angela,

00:17:48.903 --> 00:17:52.504
she always tells me
that whenever you're at her shop,

00:17:52.504 --> 00:17:54.572
business always gets better.

00:17:57.009 --> 00:18:00.378
That's because their shaved ice
is already delicious.

00:18:04.049 --> 00:18:05.451
Then...

00:18:05.451 --> 00:18:09.387
after you leave,
I'll be all alone at the inn.

00:18:09.387 --> 00:18:10.189
-

00:18:10.189 --> 00:18:13.524
Doing the work of two will be exhausting.

00:18:16.061 --> 00:18:18.097
The peak season is over.

00:18:18.097 --> 00:18:20.398
The off-season will be much easier.

00:18:23.135 --> 00:18:25.671
Why are you leaving it all to me?

00:18:25.671 --> 00:18:27.372
I'm not.

00:18:39.017 --> 00:18:42.721
In that case, let's play
that game we played before.

00:18:42.721 --> 00:18:45.890
We each ask a question,
and we both have to answer honestly.

00:18:45.890 --> 00:18:46.758
-

00:18:49.328 --> 00:18:50.728
Okay.

00:18:57.903 --> 00:19:01.038
How do you feel about me?

00:19:01.038 --> 00:19:01.739
-

00:19:08.647 --> 00:19:10.315
Feel?

00:19:11.116 --> 00:19:13.184
I feel like you should be more confident.

00:19:14.853 --> 00:19:16.721
You're such a great guy. Right?

00:19:16.721 --> 00:19:17.556
-

00:19:17.556 --> 00:19:20.224
I'm sure you'll do a great job
with the work here.

00:19:39.811 --> 00:19:42.347
Now, it's your turn to ask.

00:19:44.149 --> 00:19:46.150
I'll ask once I've thought of one.

00:19:58.325 --> 00:19:59.599
[Quan Zuo Xun Asia Tour 2026]

00:20:06.524 --> 00:20:07.658
[Traffic is being moderated]
[Try again later]

00:20:12.044 --> 00:20:13.111
- Li Wan Zhe!
- What?

00:20:13.111 --> 00:20:14.279
-

00:20:14.279 --> 00:20:16.315
Your mom wants you to help out.

00:20:16.315 --> 00:20:18.383
There are too many customers today.

00:20:18.383 --> 00:20:20.918
Wait a second, I'm busy!

00:20:25.057 --> 00:20:26.592
Busy with what?

00:20:26.592 --> 00:20:28.960
Stop bothering me, I'm buying tickets.

00:20:32.431 --> 00:20:34.499
I can't get in!

00:20:35.133 --> 00:20:37.168
How is that possible?

00:20:41.607 --> 00:20:42.941
I knew it.

00:20:42.941 --> 00:20:45.644
I've never successfully
bought a ticket in my life.

00:20:45.644 --> 00:20:47.246
- You want to go to a concert?
- Yeah.

00:20:47.246 --> 00:20:48.347
-

00:20:48.347 --> 00:20:50.415
It's his first concert in ten years.

00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:52.550
Who knows when he'll perform again?

00:20:53.418 --> 00:20:56.455
Just buy from a scalper then.

00:20:56.455 --> 00:20:58.490
I'm not buying from scalpers.

00:20:58.490 --> 00:21:01.324
It's because of those scalpers
buying up all the tickets that I can't get any.

00:21:01.324 --> 00:21:02.094
-

00:21:02.094 --> 00:21:04.629
Why should I let them profit?

00:21:05.764 --> 00:21:09.501
Forget it. I'm not a hardcore fan anyway.

00:21:09.501 --> 00:21:13.803
Just play games with me these few days
to help me forget about it.

00:21:13.803 --> 00:21:14.739
-

00:21:19.554 --> 00:21:23.331
[Quan Zuo Xun Asia Tour 2026]
[Sold Out]

00:21:28.954 --> 00:21:32.357
If you want to come, just take the boat.

00:21:32.357 --> 00:21:34.925
The island isn't big.
You won't get lost.

00:21:34.925 --> 00:21:35.626
-

00:21:37.763 --> 00:21:40.032
Turn left after getting off and walk on.

00:21:40.032 --> 00:21:42.200
You'll see a grocery store.

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:44.503
When I was a kid,
I'd go buy watermelon candies,

00:21:44.503 --> 00:21:46.838
and the owner would give me extra.

00:21:46.838 --> 00:21:49.241
His daughter often bickers with him.

00:21:49.241 --> 00:21:51.076
This is their daily routine.

00:21:51.076 --> 00:21:53.045
Sleeping in the morning and at night.

00:21:53.045 --> 00:21:54.413
- You brat!
- You're really...

00:21:54.413 --> 00:21:56.648
What should I do if I can't write a song?

00:21:56.648 --> 00:21:58.383
Excuse me.

00:21:58.383 --> 00:21:59.918
- How much is the candy?
- This one?

00:21:59.918 --> 00:22:02.352
- This one... Take your pick.
- Okay.

00:22:02.352 --> 00:22:03.055
-

00:22:03.055 --> 00:22:04.623
Since it's your first time here...

00:22:04.623 --> 00:22:05.623
Yes, it's my first time.

00:22:05.623 --> 00:22:08.025
Buy ten, get one free.

00:22:10.228 --> 00:22:11.296
Wan Zhe's house

00:22:11.296 --> 00:22:14.433
is on the corner of the shopping street
across from the pier.

00:22:14.433 --> 00:22:16.301
His mom's name is Angela.

00:22:16.301 --> 00:22:19.170
You should call her "Big Sister."

00:22:24.276 --> 00:22:26.810
At the end of the road,
is a hidden gem only locals know about.

00:22:26.810 --> 00:22:28.347
-

00:22:28.347 --> 00:22:30.749
It's also Wan Zhe's and my secret base.

00:22:30.749 --> 00:22:32.951
We call it the Seaweed Platform,

00:22:32.951 --> 00:22:37.022
because it has a lot of moss and seaweed.

00:22:37.022 --> 00:22:40.157
Whenever we're stressed out and want to relax, we come here.

00:22:40.157 --> 00:22:40.758
-

00:22:40.758 --> 00:22:41.425
-

00:22:58.910 --> 00:23:03.681
You can close your eyes and count "142857".

00:23:05.283 --> 00:23:09.587
142857.

00:23:10.522 --> 00:23:14.425
142857.

00:23:22.267 --> 00:23:24.269
After riding along the coast for 10 minutes,

00:23:24.269 --> 00:23:26.705
you'll see an old Western-style building.

00:23:26.705 --> 00:23:30.509
There's a sign at the entrance,
"Home is He-re".

00:23:30.509 --> 00:23:34.412
It's named that way so guests feel
that no matter where they're from...

00:23:34.412 --> 00:23:35.447
-

00:23:35.447 --> 00:23:39.951
or why they've come here, they'll feel at home.

00:23:39.951 --> 00:23:44.222
As if you've never left.

00:23:52.597 --> 00:23:55.100
Why is your exam paper swimming with turtles?

00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:58.087
Drawing turtles make me really happy.

00:24:15.987 --> 00:24:18.023
Excuse me.

00:24:18.023 --> 00:24:20.391
Is anyone here?

00:24:40.412 --> 00:24:42.280
Hello.

00:24:42.280 --> 00:24:44.082
Welcome.

00:24:44.082 --> 00:24:45.317
It's very beautiful, right?

00:24:45.317 --> 00:24:46.718
Let us know if you need a tour.

00:24:46.718 --> 00:24:48.854
Come here. Why did you
take so long for groceries?

00:24:48.854 --> 00:24:51.289
Hurry up and help me with the computer entry.

00:24:51.957 --> 00:24:53.658
What's wrong?

00:24:53.658 --> 00:24:56.661
You're alone today, and there's tons to do.

00:24:57.729 --> 00:24:59.363
What do you mean?

00:25:00.332 --> 00:25:01.700
Chen Hao Wei is gone.

00:25:01.700 --> 00:25:03.668
He didn't tell you?

00:25:03.668 --> 00:25:06.470
I think he left something for you.
Take a look.

00:25:06.470 --> 00:25:07.171
-

00:25:13.645 --> 00:25:15.547
Thank you.

00:25:15.547 --> 00:25:17.214
Take care.

00:25:19.451 --> 00:25:22.384
If you want to see him off,
it's not too late to go to the pier now.

00:25:22.384 --> 00:25:22.920
-

00:25:25.490 --> 00:25:27.625
I'll be back to help you
with the computer later.

00:26:05.330 --> 00:26:07.865
One ticket, please. Thank you.

00:26:09.868 --> 00:26:11.770
Chen Hao Wei.

00:26:11.770 --> 00:26:13.804
Give me five minutes.

00:26:14.940 --> 00:26:16.575
Let me buy my ticket first.

00:26:16.575 --> 00:26:18.009
Wait.

00:26:18.009 --> 00:26:20.912
Excuse me, he'll come back
for the ticket later.

00:26:20.912 --> 00:26:23.048
Just five minutes.

00:26:23.048 --> 00:26:24.582
Please.

00:26:28.853 --> 00:26:31.322
Just say whatever you have to say.

00:26:35.327 --> 00:26:38.428
Can you stay?

00:26:38.428 --> 00:26:38.996
-

00:26:44.235 --> 00:26:46.771
I can't postpone my work anymore.

00:26:50.475 --> 00:26:53.777
What if I say I like you?

00:26:53.777 --> 00:26:54.178
-

00:26:59.384 --> 00:27:01.318
I only see you as a friend.

00:27:04.923 --> 00:27:07.258
If you only see me as a friend,

00:27:07.258 --> 00:27:09.894
why did you kiss me that night we were drunk?

00:27:13.398 --> 00:27:15.633
I didn't want to hurt you.

00:27:16.901 --> 00:27:19.370
So, you're not even going to say goodbye?

00:27:21.473 --> 00:27:23.808
You already lost that person back then.

00:27:23.808 --> 00:27:26.243
Are you going to give up on me again?

00:27:30.382 --> 00:27:32.149
Are you done?

00:27:35.654 --> 00:27:37.221
Chen Hao Wei.

00:27:39.357 --> 00:27:41.125
Answer me.

00:27:48.967 --> 00:27:51.502
He Xiang Yong is the one I can't let go of.

00:27:53.104 --> 00:27:55.607
The one I've always loved is He Xiang Yong.

00:27:55.607 --> 00:27:57.441
Do you understand now?

00:27:59.110 --> 00:28:01.812
I saw his shadow in you.

00:28:03.581 --> 00:28:06.750
That's why I'm sure
he's always been in my heart.

00:28:08.486 --> 00:28:10.654
I mistook you for him.
I fell for you for a moment.

00:28:10.654 --> 00:28:11.322
-

00:28:11.322 --> 00:28:13.924
Are you okay with that?

00:28:16.327 --> 00:28:18.529
It's okay.

00:28:19.931 --> 00:28:22.299
You can keep loving him.

00:28:23.201 --> 00:28:25.803
You can even treat me as him.

00:28:32.310 --> 00:28:34.345
Chen Hao Wei.

00:28:34.345 --> 00:28:35.847
I am him.

00:28:35.847 --> 00:28:38.248
I've liked you since ten years ago.
The one who loved you was always me.

00:28:38.248 --> 00:28:38.883
-

00:28:38.883 --> 00:28:40.652
You were the star of the school,
while I was an outcast.

00:28:40.652 --> 00:28:41.886
I had the worst grades in school.

00:28:41.886 --> 00:28:43.588
We skipped class together
and got caught by the teacher together.

00:28:43.588 --> 00:28:44.923
You tutored me, and I taught you to draw.

00:28:44.923 --> 00:28:46.458
You said I had the hands of Takehiko Inoue.

00:28:46.458 --> 00:28:48.859
- I gave you the drawing for your birthday.
- Enough! That's enough!

00:28:50.495 --> 00:28:52.463
Stop talking.

00:28:55.734 --> 00:28:58.203
I know you are close to him.

00:28:58.203 --> 00:29:00.838
He shared everything with you.

00:29:03.641 --> 00:29:06.377
But feelings don't work that way.

00:29:06.377 --> 00:29:08.846
You have your own life to live.

00:29:10.982 --> 00:29:13.717
You don't need to become him for me.

00:29:14.452 --> 00:29:17.188
I've already hurt him once before.

00:29:17.188 --> 00:29:19.624
This time, I don't want
anyone else to get hurt.

00:29:19.624 --> 00:29:20.892
Hao Wei.

00:29:20.892 --> 00:29:22.127
Chen Hao Wei, please don't go.

00:29:22.127 --> 00:29:23.127
- I'm begging you, don't go.
- Don't stop me.

00:29:23.127 --> 00:29:24.795
Chen Hao Wei!

00:29:25.964 --> 00:29:29.000
You clearly feel that I'm him, don't you?

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.869
Why don't you believe in yourself?

00:29:30.869 --> 00:29:33.070
Chen Hao Wei.

00:29:38.028 --> 00:29:46.001
[Epilogue]

00:29:47.919 --> 00:29:50.054
You've only slept for a few minutes
and you're already drawing.

00:29:50.054 --> 00:29:51.856
Didn't I tell you to study?

00:29:51.856 --> 00:29:54.025
I'll study in a bit.

00:29:54.025 --> 00:29:55.627
What are you drawing?

00:29:55.627 --> 00:29:57.295
Wait.

00:29:57.295 --> 00:29:58.796
Hold on.

00:30:01.065 --> 00:30:03.201
I've been practicing portraits lately.

00:30:03.201 --> 00:30:04.302
- Portrait practice?
- Yeah.

00:30:04.302 --> 00:30:05.470
-

00:30:05.470 --> 00:30:07.505
I'm leaving now. Bye.

00:30:07.505 --> 00:30:10.041
He Xiang Yong.

00:30:10.041 --> 00:30:12.109
Don't give up on drawing.

00:30:13.545 --> 00:30:15.413
Why say that all of a sudden?

00:30:15.413 --> 00:30:18.281
Because that is what you truly love to do.

00:30:18.281 --> 00:30:19.383
-

00:30:20.552 --> 00:30:24.122
I want to follow your drawings,
forever and ever.

00:30:24.122 --> 00:30:26.123
I'll always be your number one fan.

00:30:57.255 --> 00:30:58.623
Because he wanted to take my ticket.

00:30:58.623 --> 00:31:01.558
If I die like this,
you'll remember me for the rest of your life.

00:31:01.558 --> 00:31:02.393
-

00:31:03.094 --> 00:31:04.995
If we're going to walk together,

00:31:05.964 --> 00:31:07.965
let's stay with each other for a lifetime.

00:31:10.535 --> 00:31:13.270
I wonder how long the happiness gained

00:31:14.372 --> 00:31:16.974
from making a wish can actually last.